```text id="r8c6qe"
same thing
```

Students learn:

```text id="x3c9qe"
identify character
→ examine actions
→ infer traits
→ analyze perspective
→ support with evidence
```

This develops:

* empathy
* inferential thinking
* literary analysis
* comprehension
* perspective-taking

